  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/9e304f40909be5449ca366de9141ca2a.avif?t=1760077706\" width=1280 height=720 /></span>What is <strong>Deep Space Rush</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Space Rush</strong> - a  game from BUG-Studio representing hardcore-endless Sci-fi platformer, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >which generates new levels on the go! Each new level will not be like the past!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/4d789c161fe9f17440441546242cc9c4.avif?t=1760077706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras_big/4d789c161fe9f17440441546242cc9c4.webp?t=1760077706 width=1560 height=878 /></span>What's the game about? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are one of the members of the <strong>DeTeam</strong> team, which controls the safety of scientific stations, which are various experiments of scientists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If there was a leak of the virus and everyone at the station got infected, it's your time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your gun, jump into the spaceship and go to a new sweep!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful... The <strong>DeTeam</strong> team is top secret! If you die, no one will remember you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/1a4e61a8ec85479bfbb79fc8d44c07eb.avif?t=1760077706\" width=549 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fully generated levels, traps, monsters! It will be fun, interesting and challenging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Ability to buy and pump guns and improvements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic and challenging gameplay! Are you sure you can?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic soundtrack by HateBit! Turn it up!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/9e304f40909be5449ca366de9141ca2a.avif?t=1760077706\" width=1280 height=720 /></span>What is <strong>Deep Space Rush</strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Space Rush</strong> - a  game from BUG-Studio representing hardcore-endless Sci-fi platformer, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >which generates new levels on the go! Each new level will not be like the past!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/4d789c161fe9f17440441546242cc9c4.avif?t=1760077706\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras_big/4d789c161fe9f17440441546242cc9c4.webp?t=1760077706 width=1560 height=878 /></span>What's the game about? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are one of the members of the <strong>DeTeam</strong> team, which controls the safety of scientific stations, which are various experiments of scientists.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If there was a leak of the virus and everyone at the station got infected, it's your time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab your gun, jump into the spaceship and go to a new sweep!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful... The <strong>DeTeam</strong> team is top secret! If you die, no one will remember you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/853040/extras/1a4e61a8ec85479bfbb79fc8d44c07eb.avif?t=1760077706\" width=549 height=286 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fully generated levels, traps, monsters! It will be fun, interesting and challenging!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Ability to buy and pump guns and improvements!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic and challenging gameplay! Are you sure you can?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Dynamic soundtrack by HateBit! Turn it up!</p>",
